# Faz 3: Paper Trading Motorları + SQL Persistence — Detaylı Uygulama Planı

## Mevcut Durum (Faz 1-2 Tamamlandı)

**Zaten var:**
- `ITradingEngine` interface — Application/Abstractions ✅
- `ITradeLogger` interface — Application/Abstractions ✅  
- `Trade`, `Position`, `Portfolio` entity'leri — Domain/Trading ✅
- `Signal`, `MarketRegime`, `SignalDirection` — Domain/Trading ✅
- `Error` types (PortfolioInsufficient vs.) — Domain/Common ✅
- `InMemoryCandleBuffer`, `IndicatorCalculator`, `FairValueCalculator`, `PositionSizer`, `SignalGenerator` — Infrastructure ✅
- `MarketDataWorker` — Worker/Workers ✅
- `Directory.Packages.props`: EF Core 10.0.3 zaten tanımlı ✅

**Faz 3'te eklenecekler:**
- SQL persistence (AppDbContext + migrations)
- PaperPolymarketEngine + PaperBinanceEngine
- Worker service güncellemesi
- Minor: ISignalGenerator overload + InsufficientConfirmation test

---

## GÖREV 1 — Application Layer Güncellemeleri

### 1.1 ITradingEngine Interface Güncelleme
**Dosya:** `src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Application/Abstractions/ITradingEngine.cs`

Mevcut interface'e `CheckPositionsAsync` ekle:

```csharp
using Traxon.CryptoTrader.Domain.Common;
using Traxon.CryptoTrader.Domain.Market;
using Traxon.CryptoTrader.Domain.Trading;

namespace Traxon.CryptoTrader.Application.Abstractions;

public interface ITradingEngine
{
    string EngineName { get; }

    Task<Result<Trade>>                OpenPositionAsync(Signal signal, CancellationToken ct = default);
    Task<Result<Trade>>                ClosePositionAsync(Guid tradeId, string reason, CancellationToken ct = default);
    Task<Result<IReadOnlyList<Trade>>> GetOpenTradesAsync(CancellationToken ct = default);
    Task<Result<Portfolio>>            GetPortfolioAsync(CancellationToken ct = default);
    Task<Result<bool>>                 IsReadyAsync(CancellationToken ct = default);
    /// <summary>
    /// Her candle kapanışında çağrılır. 
    /// PaperBinanceEngine: SL/TP kontrolü.
    /// PaperPolymarketEngine: Resolution süresi dolmuş mu kontrolü.
    /// </summary>
